716
00:40:08,450 --> 00:40:09,060
Itu...

717
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:11,170
Aku punya tangan dan kaki,

718
00:40:11,460 --> 00:40:12,650
tidak perlu dilayani orang lain.

719
00:40:22,700 --> 00:40:23,740
